wikimedia-copyrightwarning:
Na ö'irö'ö nifabö'önimö andre, fao dödöu ba  [https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Policy:Terms_of_Use Terms of Use], ba fao göi dödöu (tebai mufangawuli furi) wame'e halöŵömö ba [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Text_of_Creative_Commons_Attribution-ShareAlike_3.0_Unported_License CC BY-SA 3.0 License] faoma ba [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Text_of_the_GNU_Free_Documentation_License GFDL].
Fao dödömö wa sambua khai-khai ma hyperlink ma URL no tobönö ba wamaduhu'ö halöŵömö molo'ö lisensi Creative Commons.
wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked:
'''Alamat IP-mö no [[m:Special:MyLanguage/Global blocks|teba'agö moroi ba wiki fefu]].'''

Same fomba'agö $1 ($2).
Börö "$3".

* Tebörögö womba'agö: $4
* Ahori womba'agö: $5

Alamat IP-mö iada'a $6
Faogö fefu nisura andrö yaŵa na ösura wanofu.

Na faduhu dödöu wa no sala woba'agö ya'ugö, ae faigi nönö-nönö informasi ba instruktsi ba [[m:Special:MyLanguage/No open proxies|No open proxies]] global policy.

Na lö'ö, tola öfahuhuosi womba'agö andre [[m:Steward requests/Global|sura wangandrö fambatimba ba Meta-Wiki]].
wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked-xff:
'''Sambua ma töra server proksi ni'aluimö no [[m:Special:MyLanguage/Global blocks|toba'agö global]]'''

Somba'agö $1 ($2).
Börö "$3".

* i'otarai ba $4
* irugi ba $5

Alamat proksi niba'agö $6.
Fa'oli fefu da'a yaŵa na ösura wanofumö.

Na molo'ö ya'ugö no fasala wa toba'agö ndra'ugö, so nönö informasi ba instruksi ba gangetula global [[m:Special:MyLanguage/No open proxies|Lö proksi si teboka]].
Ma zui [[m:Steward requests/Global|fahuhuosi womba'agö andre yaŵa ba Meta-Wiki]].
